snippet.title: You do Fear?💓 - Determinable Unstable
snippet.description:
Is it wrong to try to pick up Girls in a Forest?
Visual Novel Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLx_GoXwrHSqFGCRu_muBtIiVVCJ4IP5ZL
A big thanks to the artist Ray-Kbys~

Edited, no commentary (for more immersion) gameplay I recorded for entertainment purposes and to brighten our days, scenes which we can revisit without playing the whole game again~
